{
  "stem": "1901.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we had a good mixture, because like what I found out much later here-- in Poland, it was so much different between people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In language, Yiddish, we couldn't speak Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't even know it existed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were very, very assimilated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had even in my family three uncles were mixed married, before I was born, really.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fortunate, in a way, because they survived the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, they-- and they had no children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But no, we had no-- no hardship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was our downfall, really, because we never took it serious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Holland was not in the first war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were neutral.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we never took that serious, like what we read in the papers in those days, that they would come to Holland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They never gave it a second thought.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was discussed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had even family in England.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, far family, and I easy could have gone to England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I even had in, when I finished school, I played in a band.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And accidentally was in Belgian, band, and I was 18, 19-- 19 years, turning 19.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that band went from Holland to Switzerland end of 1939.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could have gone with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would have been out of the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother thought I was too young, and I stayed home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because it was not-- no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I said, we never expect anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't believe it, what you read in the paper, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and of course, we had anti-Semitism, but different.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, never, never.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tell you-- I'll give you one-- one-- I've told it many, many times.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had one friend, and he played in my band.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he played the trombone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a very tall fellow.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
